    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/f2a223d96dfc947e50ddd2b85e1d6024.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/c8115b746729d8a7bdc2a834de176f72.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/c8115b746729d8a7bdc2a834de176f72.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/c8115b746729d8a7bdc2a834de176f72.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beacon's Bluff 是一个2D叙事驱动的恐怖冒险点击游戏.<br>你接受了在一个神秘、孤立的灯塔当灯塔管理员的工作.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/4c89b007e4671d69f0306b125bb9108c.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/4c89b007e4671d69f0306b125bb9108c.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/4c89b007e4671d69f0306b125bb9108c.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>保持灯塔的光亮，并通过解决引人入胜的谜题来生存下去. 沉浸在这个识别性的恐怖冒险游戏——Beacon's Bluff 是 Story Machine Shorts 系列的第一部.<br><br><strong>你的守夜现在开始</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]等待你的是夜班[]完成动态的灯塔任务以保持灯亮[]无论你做什么，不要让灯熄灭。否则，船只可能会碰撞。或者更糟...[]你负责从午夜到早晨6点的灯塔工作<li>生存下你的班次即可胜利</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/6363a7d32da414d609a18b83938dd58f.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/6363a7d32da414d609a18b83938dd58f.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/6363a7d32da414d609a18b83938dd58f.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
